  rounds:
  - victimMessage: "Alo, ai \u0111\u1EA5y? \u0110ang b\u1EADn h\u1ECDp, n\xF3i nhanh!"
    scriptToType: Chao anh Bao, toi la can bo ben Cuc Thue. Ho so cua cong ty anh
      dang co van de nghiem trong.
    timeLimit: 1
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: "Em ch\xE1n s\u1ED1ng r\u1ED3i \u0111\xFAng kh\xF4ng, chat
      nhanh l\xEAn coi"
  - victimMessage: "Thu\u1EBF m\xE1 g\xEC? K\u1EBF to\xE1n nh\xE0 t\xF4i lo h\u1EBFt
      r\u1ED3i, \u0111\u1EEBng c\xF3 v\u1EDB v\u1EA9n."
    scriptToType: Chung toi da nam duoc bang chung anh tron thue 3 nam nay. Ngay
      mai se co doan thanh tra xuong.
    timeLimit: 1
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "G\xF5 nhanh l\xEAn! L\xE3o n\xE0y s\u1EAFp c\xFAp m\xE1y
      r\u1ED3i!"
  - victimMessage: "\u1EA4y ch\u1EBFt... anh l\xE0 c\xE1n b\u1ED9 n\xE0o \u0111\u1EA5y?
      C\xF3 c\xE1ch n\xE0o ch\xE2m ch\u01B0\u1EDBc cho doanh nghi\u1EC7p kh\xF4ng
      anh?"
    scriptToType: Neu anh muon em chuyen nay, hay chuyen ngay 50 trieu vao tai khoan
      cua lanh dao de lo lot ho so.
    timeLimit: 1
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "50 tri\u1EC7u \xE1? Cho t\xF4i xin 1 ng\xE0y thu x\u1EBFp \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      kh\xF4ng?"
    scriptToType: Nhanh len, giam doc sap ky quyet dinh roi. Chuyen ngay de toi con
      rut ho so cua anh ra!
    timeLimit: 1
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "M\xE0y g\xF5 ch\u1EADm tao ch\xEDch \u0111i\u1EC7n b\xE2y
      gi\u1EDD"
  - victimMessage: "R\u1ED3i r\u1ED3i t\xF4i chuy\u1EC3n r\u1ED3i! Anh ki\u1EC3m
      tra gi\xFAp t\xF4i v\u1EDBi!"
    scriptToType: Da nhan duoc tien. Anh yen tam, moi chuyen da duoc giai quyet on
      thoa. Xoa tin nhan nay di.
